<h4><a href="https://www.thepaper.cn/newsDetail_forward_10039918">新荣耀董事会组成出炉</a></h4>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1380113" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/horizontal.jpeg" alt="" width="1320" height="742" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/horizontal.jpeg 1320w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/horizontal-360x202.jpeg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/horizontal-768x432.jpeg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/horizontal-1024x576.jpeg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1320px) 100vw, 1320px" /></p>
<p>澎湃消息，接盘荣耀的新公司深圳市智信新信息技术有限公司（深圳智信）董事会成员出炉。其董事会成员包括：董事长兼法定代表人万飚、董事总经理赵明、董事方飞、董事彭求恩、董事李山林、董事舒洪峰。</p>
<p>新荣耀的董事会除了舒洪峰是深圳智慧城市集团的代表，赵明是原荣耀总裁，其他都是华为空降干部。其中，万飚原本是华为消费者业务首席运营官、彭求恩原本是华为消费者业务 CFO，方飞是华为第二手机产品线总裁，李山林是华为集团东北欧地区部人力资源部部长。</p>
<h4><a href="https://finance.sina.com.cn/stock/usstock/c/2020-11-18/doc-iiznctke2128431.shtml">波音 737 Max 在美停飞令解除</a></h4>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1380114" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/marquee.jpg" alt="" width="1280" height="720" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/marquee.jpg 1280w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/marquee-360x203.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/marquee-768x432.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/marquee-1024x576.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1280px) 100vw, 1280px" /></p>
<p>新浪财经消息，美国联邦航空管理局（FAA）解除了波音 737 Max 的停飞令，这标志着美国历史上持续期最长的客机停飞结束，并为世界各地的航空公司和其他监管机构复飞该机型奠定了基础。</p>
<p>FAA 要求波音修复在两次空难中失控的安全系统，以及在审查中发现的其它缺陷；此外，飞行员也需就 737 Max 机型参与新的培训，侧重于事故中出现的问题。</p>
<h4>最新疫情数字</h4>
<p><strong>国内（不含港澳台）部分已公布数据</strong>：11 月 18 日，上海新增 1 例境外输入确诊病例；广西新增确诊病例 2 例、无症状感染者 2 例，均为境外输入；山东新增境外输入无症状感染者 1 例；内蒙古新增境外输入确诊病例 1 例。</p>
<p><strong>香港</strong>：11 月 17 日，新增 9 例确诊病例，其中 6 例为输入性病例。香港确诊病例累计 5479 例。</p>
<p><strong>海外</strong>：截至 11 月 19 日 7 时，海外累计确诊病例 56,125,178 例，累计死亡 1,342,640 例，累计治愈 38,721,229 例。</p>
<h4><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1293888" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/keji.png" alt="" width="1715" height="300" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/keji.png 1715w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/keji-360x63.png 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/keji-768x134.png 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/keji-1024x179.png 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1715px) 100vw, 1715px" /></h4>
<h4><a href="https://twitter.com/markgurman/status/1328924718603272192">MagSafe Duo 充电器无法以 15W 功率为 iPhone 充电</a></h4>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1380115" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/dbohn_201109_4283_0003.0.0.jpg" alt="" width="920" height="613" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/dbohn_201109_4283_0003.0.0.jpg 920w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/dbohn_201109_4283_0003.0.0-360x240.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/dbohn_201109_4283_0003.0.0-768x512.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 920px) 100vw, 920px" /></p>
<p>《彭博社》的 Mark Gurman 指出，苹果在更新后的<a href="https://www.apple.com/shop/product/MHXF3AM/A/magsafe-duo-charger">官方 MagSafe Duo 页面</a>表示，这款充电器无法以 15W 功率为 iPhone 充电。</p>
<p>当搭配 20W 电源适配器使用时，MagSafe Duo 为 iPhone 充电功率最高为 11W；搭配 27W 或以上电源适配器使用时，充电功率最高为 14W，均无法达到 iPhone 12 系列（iPhone 12 mini 除外）用普通 MagSafe 时可达到的最高 15W。</p>
<h4><a href="https://www.macrumors.com/2020/11/18/apple-releases-ios-14-2-revised-iphone-12/">苹果发布修改版 iOS 14.2</a></h4>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1380116" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/iOS14.2on-Phone-Feature-2.jpg" alt="" width="1600" height="899" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/iOS14.2on-Phone-Feature-2.jpg 1600w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/iOS14.2on-Phone-Feature-2-360x202.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/iOS14.2on-Phone-Feature-2-768x432.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/iOS14.2on-Phone-Feature-2-1024x575.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1600px) 100vw, 1600px" /></p>
<p>MacRumors 消息，苹果推送了一个修改版的 iOS 14.2，此前未更新到 iOS 14.2 的 iPhone 12 用户会收到该系统推送。目前暂不明确苹果推出这个新版本的目的，也许是为了修复一些漏洞或安装问题。</p>
<h4><a href="https://www.sohu.com/a/432703716_115565">vivo 发布 OriginOS</a></h4>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1380117" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/OOS-1-1.jpg" alt="" width="720" height="471" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/OOS-1-1.jpg 720w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/OOS-1-1-360x236.jpg 360w" sizes="(max-width: 720px) 100vw, 720px" /></p>
<p>搜狐科技消息，vivo 昨天发布了手机操作系统 OriginOS。OriginOS 采用了华容桌面与原子组件的设计元素。</p>
<p>华容网格是一种新的桌面网格体系，用户可通过基础单元创造出最多 26 种不同组合。原子通知则把通知直接显示到了桌面 APP 上，无需打开 APP 即可在第一层级上看到信息通知。原子件组库是针对于 OriginOS 的桌面所特有的桌面 APP 组合方式，可以提供简单便捷的调取方式。</p>
<h3><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1293889" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/dagongs.png" alt="" width="1029" height="180" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/dagongs.png 1029w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/dagongs-360x63.png 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/dagongs-768x134.png 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/dagongs-1024x179.png 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1029px) 100vw, 1029px" /></h3>
<h4><a href="https://www.apple.com.cn/newsroom/2020/11/apple-announces-app-store-small-business-program/">苹果将减半对小型企业征收的 App Store 佣金</a></h4>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1380118" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/deve.jpg" alt="" width="702" height="448" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/deve.jpg 702w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/deve-360x230.jpg 360w" sizes="(max-width: 702px) 100vw, 702px" /></p>
<p>苹果宣布推出 App Store 小型企业计划。在上一个日历年的收益 100 万美元以下的开发者将可参与该计划，享受 App Store 佣金降至 15% 的优惠。此前，App Store 的佣金费率均为 30%。</p>
<p>苹果表示，希望借该计划在疫情下帮助和鼓励小型企业和开发者，使其「获得更多资源，用于投资和发展在 App Store 生态系统中的业务」。该计划将于 2021 年 1 月 1 日正式启动。</p>
<h4><a href="https://finance.sina.com.cn/tech/2020-11-19/doc-iiznezxs2585121.shtml">B 站发布 Q3 财报，同比增长 74%</a></h4>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1380119" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/5d09df30f99c4a038aaf314df175adcc.jpg" alt="" width="2160" height="1440" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/5d09df30f99c4a038aaf314df175adcc.jpg 2160w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/5d09df30f99c4a038aaf314df175adcc-360x240.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/5d09df30f99c4a038aaf314df175adcc-768x512.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/5d09df30f99c4a038aaf314df175adcc-1024x683.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 2160px) 100vw, 2160px" /></p>
<p>DoNews 消息，哔哩哔哩发布了截至 2020 年 9 月 30 日的第三季度未经审计的财务报告。财报显示，B 站三季度营收为 32.3 亿元人民币，同比增长 74%，超市场预期。</p>
<p>社区月均活跃用户同比增长 54% 达 1.97 亿，移动端月均活跃用户同比增长 61% 达 1.84 亿；本季度月均付费用户数同比增长 89％ 至 1500 万，付费率从去年同期的 6.2％ 提升至 7.6％。</p>
<p>第三季度调整后的非美国会计通用准则的净亏损为 9.9 亿元人民币，去年同期为 3.43 亿元。</p>
<h4><a href="https://www.yicai.com/news/100843159.html">虎牙和中国传媒大学共同成立电竞研究中心</a></h4>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1380120" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/5f7f8ab1cfb77bce0bc4a2dd537c91eb.jpg" alt="" width="1190" height="669" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/5f7f8ab1cfb77bce0bc4a2dd537c91eb.jpg 1190w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/5f7f8ab1cfb77bce0bc4a2dd537c91eb-360x202.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/5f7f8ab1cfb77bce0bc4a2dd537c91eb-768x432.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/5f7f8ab1cfb77bce0bc4a2dd537c91eb-1024x576.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1190px) 100vw, 1190px" /></p>
<p>《第一财经》消息，虎牙公司与中国传媒大学昨天宣布达成深度战略合作，共同成立中传虎牙电竞研究中心。</p>
<p>双方将通过校企联合培养中国未来各类电竞人才，进一步推动中国精品电竞品牌升级，打造中国电竞产业生态，并以更为完善的行业标准促进电竞产业蓬勃发展。双方推动举办的首届北京国际大学生电竞节也正式启动。</p>
<h4><a href="https://m.weibo.cn/status/4572712703629508?">微博就违规收集使用个人信息致歉：正在进行内部整改</a></h4>
<p>新浪微博昨晚发公告称，「11 月 14 日 app 违法违规收集使用个人信息治理工作组发布通告，显示微博 app 存在两个 ‘个人信息收集使用’ 方面的问题，微博对此深表歉意」。</p>
<p>微博表示现正在进行内部整改，保证在限期内按主管部门要求更新隐私协议内容，梳理用户隐私相关权限的合理性，保护用户隐私权益不受侵害。</p>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1380121" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/weibo.jpg" alt="" width="724" height="800" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/weibo.jpg 724w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/weibo-360x398.jpg 360w" sizes="(max-width: 724px) 100vw, 724px" /></p>
<h4>长安通开始支持 Apple Pay</h4>
<p>Apple Pay 正式支持⻓安通，用户可以使用 Apple Pay 快捷交通模式便捷出行， 在西安乘坐公交和地铁。西安是 Apple Pay 快捷交通卡在中国大陆地区支持的第 10 个城市。Apple Pay 将可享受和实体交通卡同样本地优惠政策。</p>
<h3><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1357461" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/citylife.png" alt="" width="1029" height="153" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/citylife.png 1029w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/citylife-360x54.png 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/citylife-768x114.png 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/citylife-1024x152.png 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1029px) 100vw, 1029px" /></h3>
<h4><a href="https://edition.cnn.com/2020/11/16/business/pepsi-bottle-redesign/index.html">百事重新设计了用了 30 年饮料瓶</a></h4>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1380122" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/201116092242-20201116-pepsi-dew-sierra-mist-exlarge-169.jpg" alt="" width="780" height="438" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/201116092242-20201116-pepsi-dew-sierra-mist-exlarge-169.jpg 780w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/201116092242-20201116-pepsi-dew-sierra-mist-exlarge-169-360x202.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/201116092242-20201116-pepsi-dew-sierra-mist-exlarge-169-768x431.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 780px) 100vw, 780px" /></p>
<p>作为公司可持续发展项目一部分，百事重新设计了在美国用了将近 30 年的 2L 装汽水瓶。</p>
<p>全新设计的瓶子在保持瓶身塑料用量不变的情况下，将瓶子下半部分设计得更窄，更符合人体力学，握感更佳；而瓶子上的塑料标签用料则减少了 24%。</p>
<p>此外，瓶子窄身部分还成为了不同产品展示其品牌差异性的地方。譬如，百事可乐采用了浪形螺纹、激浪自采用了类似闪电的图案。</p>
<h4><a href="https://hypebeast.cn/2020/11/muji-yo-no-ie-minimal-tiny-home-opening-news">无印良品推出新「阳の家」迷你屋</a></h4>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1380123" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/muji-yo-no-ie-minimal-tiny-home-opening-news-1.jpg" alt="" width="840" height="560" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/muji-yo-no-ie-minimal-tiny-home-opening-news-1.jpg 840w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/muji-yo-no-ie-minimal-tiny-home-opening-news-1-360x240.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/muji-yo-no-ie-minimal-tiny-home-opening-news-1-768x512.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 840px) 100vw, 840px" /></p>
<p>Hypebeast 消息，无印良品推出了新的「阳の家」迷你屋，位于日本山口县，全屋不含外部设施占地 80 平方米。</p>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1380124" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/muji-yo-no-ie-minimal-tiny-home-opening-news-3.jpg" alt="" width="840" height="560" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/muji-yo-no-ie-minimal-tiny-home-opening-news-3.jpg 840w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/muji-yo-no-ie-minimal-tiny-home-opening-news-3-360x240.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/muji-yo-no-ie-minimal-tiny-home-opening-news-3-768x512.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 840px) 100vw, 840px" /></p>
<p>全屋表面采用雪松木打造而成，木材本身将随着时间经过印上岁月的痕迹，令住户能够感受到真正自然生活。</p>
<h4><a href="http://news.mtime.com/2020/11/18/1604769.html">《怪物猎人》国内定档</a></h4>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1380125" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/101157.31777934_620X620.jpg" alt="" width="620" height="876" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/101157.31777934_620X620.jpg 620w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/101157.31777934_620X620-360x509.jpg 360w" sizes="(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px" /></p>
<p>时光网消息，游戏改编片《怪物猎人》宣布国内定档 12 月 4 日。</p>
<p>《怪物猎人》讲述了指挥官阿蒂米斯所在的军事小队意外落入异世，联手神秘猎人搏命求生、重返家园的刺激冒险。</p>
<h3><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1293890" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/wangyo.png" alt="" width="1029" height="180" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/wangyo.png 1029w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/wangyo-360x63.png 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/wangyo-768x134.png 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/wangyo-1024x179.png 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1029px) 100vw, 1029px" /></h3>
<h4>微信表情更新了</h4>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1380126" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/weixin.jpg" alt="" width="1027" height="300" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/weixin.jpg 1027w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/weixin-360x105.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/weixin-768x224.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/weixin-1024x299.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1027px) 100vw, 1027px" /></p>
<p>微信更新了 6 个新表情：翻白眼、666、让我看看、叹气、苦涩、裂开。</p>
<p>网友：「太喜欢了，是在过于真实了。」「又多了几个应付半熟不熟的人的表情。」「第三个请叫 ‘假装捂脸’，意思是表面看起来很同情实际为看戏。」</p>
<h3><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1357582" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/thur.png" alt="" width="1029" height="153" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/thur.png 1029w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/thur-360x54.png 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/thur-768x114.png 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/thur-1024x152.png 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1029px) 100vw, 1029px" /></h3>
<h4><a href="https://www.archdaily.cn/cn/951163/bai-jing-wu-jiu-dian-teng-ben-zhuang-jie-jian-zhu-shi-wu-suo?utm_medium=email&amp;utm_source=ArchDaily%20China&amp;utm_campaign=weekly&amp;kth=5,292,785">白井屋酒店 @ 前桥市·日本</a></h4>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1378974" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/hoet.jpg" alt="" width="1000" height="667" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/hoet.jpg 1000w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/hoet-360x240.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/hoet-768x512.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px" /></p>
<p>藤本壮介亲自负责了「白井屋酒店」的建筑和室内设计，并邀请了设计师 Michele de Lucchi，Jasper Morrison 和 Leandro Erlich 设计不同主题风格的酒店房间。</p>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1378977" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/hotelroom.jpg" alt="" width="1200" height="394" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/hotelroom.jpg 1200w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/hotelroom-360x118.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/hotelroom-768x252.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/hotelroom-1024x336.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px" /></p>
<p>酒店分为两部分——遗迹塔和绿色塔。其中，遗迹塔基于 1970 年代落成的建筑，包含 17 个主题各异的房间。</p>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1378975" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/yiji.jpg" alt="" width="1000" height="667" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/yiji.jpg 1000w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/yiji-360x240.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/yiji-768x512.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px" /></p>
<div class="editor-image-source">
<p>▲ 遗迹塔</p>
</div>
<p>绿色塔则关注于极简和绿色生态这两个概念的呈现，旨在模拟四周的起伏景观。</p>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1378976" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/lvse.jpg" alt="" width="893" height="1340" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/lvse.jpg 893w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/lvse-360x540.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/lvse-768x1152.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/lvse-682x1024.jpg 682w" sizes="(max-width: 893px) 100vw, 893px" /></p>
<div class="editor-image-source">
<p>▲ 绿色塔</p>
</div>
